{"tid":746404,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★舜宇遭沽空機構質疑財報內容","createTime":"2018-07-17T13:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T17:05:55.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"68ed29af1a6e93596d1ce58276ae354790ab4fad","tid":746404,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:43:19.000Z","msg":"舜宇光學(02382)成沽空機構GMT Research新狙擊目標！GMT Research在Twitter發文，指舜宇存在財務欺詐，當中該公司聲稱有82%的鏡頭是外部銷售，惟得18%用於模組製作，而數據顯示，模組的數量超過鏡頭的50%，意味大部分模組的鏡頭都是由外部購買，認為舜宇是透過內部銷售來誇大收入和利潤。<br />\n<br />\n舜宇股價一度跌7%，低見141.6元；現仍跌6.83%至141.9元。<br />\n<br />\n該公司回覆東網查詢指已接獲有關消息，惟暫未有進一步回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180717/bkn-20180717152615076-0717_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180717%2Fbkn-20180717152615076-0717_00842_001.html&d=eGzFkpZEALB1PzcJy8m%2FK10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=02ad1c23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180717/bkn-20180717152615076-0717_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"35097df673a6a31a2d14180bc9e230046bef005b","tid":746404,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nall phone stock need die<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa0dfb3e2941b74e0c9d035d6106e661797717c","tid":746404,"uid":42420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:04:56.000Z","msg":"出左公告澄清啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76a9db23cccc0ab2a8581a08ee586e998c038bc","tid":746404,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s